  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I hope that some of these music you'll be able to hear now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, this didn't end it with this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This crystallized later on when, during my concerts in different countries, I succeed to enrich this collection with a, a number of other musical works of, again, relatives of Jewish family that you see for one or other, a way to save some musical compositions of disappeared persons.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very few.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very few.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There are pieces, perhaps, totaling [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] maybe a couple of dozens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, I very much would like, of course, that we be able to at least, a few of them, couple of them to hear.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was hoping that they will remain in the permanent heritage of the Jewish music, of the Jewish culture of European Jews during this epoch.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this is almost one of the most beautiful monuments to this martyrs of the Jewish culture, of this very dark period of the story of Israeli, Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did a number of other things later on in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I get possibility to excel in not only with my own activity as a soloist but with my students, that-- already my students started to succeed to winning the national prizes in music.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Also I developed this very special program for children's orchestra that gave, actually, the, the live musical life and defined the musical destiny of a number of little children around the globe, around the world.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I built around 68 orchestras, children's orchestras, during more than 10 years as an adviser to UNSCO.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "United Nations Scientific and Cultural Organization.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
